{"tid":2312552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會對著見得一次面嘅人講大話？","createTime":"2020-12-05T05:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T00:33:17.000Z","uid":371041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0945ef4e2cc7e4f084367d4d242c02222710d37c","tid":2312552,"uid":371041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我平時會唔經意對住一啲自己唔會再見面嘅人講一啲大話，例如係：住嘅地方、學歷、年齡、名、職業、家庭背景......等等。<br />\n<br />\n因為個種感覺好奇怪，所以我想知有冇人會同我一樣會對住第一次見嘅人講大話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e8d202d61084196041ee8302ab57f19cf9cc19","tid":2312552,"uid":371041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ea5d639487bbeaaba547cb16b7491be4f30135","tid":2312552,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"又未至於<br />\n但唔想答嘅話，就扮聽唔到算"},{"pid":"c67ab3c17727d680a7b3f378bbd2dbbdc306bcdd","tid":2312552,"uid":30785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"我會同佢講個好普通既英文名<br />\n等佢唔記得我/搵唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc8742f539d5e972985b6b23fbf0c3127dd62f6","tid":2312552,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"講真同講大話都無乜所謂<br />\n唔講太深入咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n你唔想比人知<br />\n人地都未必想知"},{"pid":"28df60aed1234601b318eb9c0e2308a7144cc64d","tid":2312552,"uid":371041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32ea5d639487bbeaaba547cb16b7491be4f30135","tid":2312552,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"又未至於<br />\n但唔想答嘅話，就扮聽唔到算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"但有時候就係你焗住要答佢嘅情況睇下，我就會講咗啲大話搪塞敷衍個個人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"